{"tid":2171333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到快必撚狗post真係好嘔心，香港人真係永遠當人condom","createTime":"2020-08-23T23:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T06:24:43.000Z","uid":65328,"like":24,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3b60250246e48457dfc0a46ece780f07ef8f5026","tid":2171333,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:48:17.000Z","msg":"見到快必撚狗post真係好嘔心，香港人真係永遠當人condom<br />\n<br />\n見到有人撚狗覺得好正， 分分鐘過萬正評<br />\n但初選果時就屌快必唔得<br />\n呼籲投其他所謂&quot;本土派&quot;議員<br />\n<br />\n結果依班所謂&quot;本土派&quot;議員， <br />\n初選時成日浦頭，<br />\n初選結束後政府延遲選舉一年就神隱咁耐。<br />\n<br />\n有人犧牲好多野香港人就話投票不了<br />\n有人錫身繼續做泛民一樣既野就話全民要投佢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">延遲選舉班人都可以神隱收皮啦</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9eebc4ebfe1dec1d7af754ca1dd95d6c813d4947","tid":2171333,"uid":239842,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:49:19.000Z","msg":"好，下次投番佢囉咁"},{"pid":"5bfaa8368486b4adab9aba5f1e3f096e2c3db1f0","tid":2171333,"uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9eebc4ebfe1dec1d7af754ca1dd95d6c813d4947","tid":2171333,"uid":239842,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:49:19.000Z","msg":"好，下次投番佢囉咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:51:08.000Z","msg":"下次？有下次先講啦"},{"pid":"76a2a1999693aedd2c08895f31c362117f45b397","tid":2171333,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:54:04.000Z","msg":"???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef8cc31dea034b4112ea4b1ea2b933b464ee544","tid":2171333,"uid":65328,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76a2a1999693aedd2c08895f31c362117f45b397","tid":2171333,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:54:04.000Z","msg":"???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse